Contact¶

Feel free to contact me in case you run problems or allow me to identify whether PARAPROBE supplies functionalities which can cater also your APT analyses needs! In case of bug reports please send always a console prompt (see how to execute section of this manual) of the simulation run and the xml input file to assist me in diagnosing the issue.
